    "The insights provided are intended to inspire further research into addressing the security threats associated with AI agents, thereby fostering the development of more robust and secure AI agent applications.In this survey, we systematically review and analyze the threats and solutions of AI agent security based on four knowledge gaps, covering both the breadth and depth aspects.",
    "We primarily collected papers from top AI conferences, top cybersecurity conferences, and highly cited arXiv papers, spanning from January 2022 to April 2024.",
